 r←{addToCaption}YesOrNo caption;cs
⍝ Ask a Question with two buttons: "Yes" and "No"
 :If ##.G.TestFlag
     r←1
 :Else
     cs←CreateDefaultParms
     cs.okCaption←'Yes'
     cs.cancelCaption←'No'
     :If 0<⎕NC'addToCaption'
         cs.addToCaption←addToCaption
     :EndIf
     r←cs Run caption
 :EndIf
